window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dane Reynolds:</b></p> <p>President of the Savage Angels MC.</p> <p>Fierce, strong and loyal.</p> <p>He’s had his eye on Kat for a while now, and has been waiting for her to come to him. But he’s had enough of waiting.</p> <p>He’s decided it’s time to make her his.</p> <p><b>Katarina Saunders:</b></p> <p>To the world, Kat is an international rock star.</p> <p>Lead singer for The Grinders.</p> <p>Until she has an accident that ruins her career and sends her running into the mountains, away from everything and everyone.</p> <p>Will these two come together?</p> <p>Or will Kat’s savage stalker get to her first?</p> <p>From<i> USA Today</i> best-selling author Kathleen Kelly.</p>"; 
